The module consists a study tour to leading states of European Union to observe the international institutions, influencing European business environment. During the visits the main operating aspects of the institutions and their role in the business environment will be discussed. The module includes also company visits to discuss their adaptation to business environment changes.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The module gives an overview of international institutions, influencing European business environment, their main operating aspects and impacts on companies' operations.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Students acquire knowledge of business environment and communication about international, economic, political and cultural features and skills and experience for professional communication in a foreign language.
